data.description: Welcome to your turn-key dream! This home has a Modern open concept great room that has separation for function as well as high style with designer touches and custom built ins. It is the perfect floor-plan for family and entertainment! The Custom lighting elegantly showcases the custom touches throughout the home. The custom kitchen is designed with gold and black accents as well as beautiful quartz counters and high end appliances, unlike any other. Large Bedrooms are split and have walk in closets. There is plenty of storage, as well as a flex space for office/workout area. House comes mostly furnished including all kitchen appliances! Set it up as a temporary rental or move right on in. We have also included a plunge pool rendering showing you can have one built!
